WEBVTT

00:00:01.409 --> 00:00:04.351
Every other night in Japan,

00:00:04.375 --> 00:00:06.402
I step out of my apartment,

00:00:06.426 --> 00:00:09.930
I climb up a hill for 15 minutes,

00:00:09.954 --> 00:00:13.604
and then I head into my local health club,

00:00:13.628 --> 00:00:18.154
where three ping-pong tables
are set up in a studio.

00:00:18.178 --> 00:00:20.153
And space is limited,

00:00:20.177 --> 00:00:21.889
so at every table,

00:00:21.913 --> 00:00:24.843
one pair of players practices forehands,

00:00:24.867 --> 00:00:27.160
another practices backhands,

00:00:27.184 --> 00:00:30.772
and every now and then,
the balls collide in midair